      "summary": "Sanchit Jain is a Lead at Quantiphi Inc. and a certified AWS Cloud expert with deep expertise in building secure Enterprise Data Platforms. He plays a pivotal role in leading the AWS User Group Mumbai, driving community engagement and talent development through knowledge-sharing sessions and university initiatives. A recognized speaker at global forums such as AWS re:Invent and AWS Summit India, he also shares thought leadership via technical blogs on AWS services. 1. Blogs - https://blog.getsetbuild.cloud/ 2. LinkedIn - https://www.linkedin.com/in/sanchitdilipjain/ 3. AWS UserGroup Mumbai - https://www.linkedin.com/company/awsugmum 4. AWS UserGroup Data - https://www.linkedin.com/company/awsugdataindia 5. Hashicorp UserGroup Mumbai - https://www.linkedin.com/company/hug-mumbai",
